Package akka.cluster.sbr

Class SplitBrainResolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • akka.cluster.sbr.SplitBrainResolverBase
      • akka.cluster.sbr.SplitBrainResolver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Actor, Stash, StashSupport, Timers, UnrestrictedStash, RequiresMessageQueue<DequeBasedMessageQueueSemantics>
    public final class SplitBrainResolver
extends SplitBrainResolverBase
    INTERNAL API

    Unreachable members will be downed by this actor according to the given strategy. It is active on the leader node in the cluster.

    The implementation is split into two classes SplitBrainResolver and SplitBrainResolverBase to be able to unit test the logic without running cluster.
